# CALCULATOR

A simple calculator built with HTML, CSS and JavaScript.

## Features
- Basic arithmetic operations (+ - × ÷)
- Clear button
- Responsive display

## Tech Stack
- HTML
- CSS
- JavaScript

## Features
- Basic arithmetic operations (+ - × ÷)
- Clear button
- Responsive display

## UI
- Soft pink and purple color palette
- Rounded square buttons
- Clean minimal design
- Pixel font for display
- Smooth button press animation